        "footer_faq": "FAQ",
        "footer_kvkk": "KVKK Text",
        "pricing_faq_subtitle": "FAQ",
        "pricing_faq_title": "Frequently Asked Questions",
        "pricing_faq_q_0": "How long does website design take?",
        "pricing_faq_a_0": "Although it depends on the scope, delivery times can be 1–3 weeks for corporate sites, and down to 3 days for simpler landing sites. Unlike agencies that take months, I work fast and directly.",
        "pricing_faq_q_1": "How are 3D animation packages priced?",
        "pricing_faq_a_1": "I offer three main packages: Basic ($500) — up to 10-second 1080p loop or render; Standard ($1,000) — 15–30 seconds, 4K, sound design included; Gold ($2,000) — up to 60 seconds of cinematic production, source files, and unlimited revisions. For web design pricing, I suggest contacting me directly.",
        "pricing_faq_q_2": "Do you work with clients outside of Ankara?",
        "pricing_faq_a_2": "Yes, although I am based in Ankara, I provide remote services across Turkey and globally. In particular, I offer English SEO and multilingual website solutions for furniture manufacturers and industrial companies wanting to expand to international markets.",
        "pricing_faq_q_3": "Can I get a website built as a lawyer or law firm without violating the advertising ban?",
        "pricing_faq_a_3": "Yes. I design websites that are fully compliant with Legal Profession Act Article 55 and relevant regulations in Turkey. I construct sites with corporate identities, practice areas, and blog infrastructures that bring organic clients without crossing the boundary of 'advertising for the purpose of attracting customers.'",
        "pricing_faq_q_4": "How many websites have you launched?",
        "pricing_faq_a_4": "I have launched over 100 websites to date. I have collaborated with institutions like Goethe Institut, Paribu, TRT Belgesel, and the Ministry of Trade; additionally, I have served many law firms, industrial manufacturers, and entrepreneurs.",
        "pricing_faq_q_5": "Do you only do design, or is SEO included?",
        "pricing_faq_a_5": "I offer both design and SEO. My services include local SEO (Google Maps optimization), B2B SEO, international SEO, and setting up blog/article infrastructures. Working at the intersection of design and SEO strategy is my core approach.",
        "pricing_faq_q_6": "How do we start a project?",
        "pricing_faq_a_6": "You can contact me via the contact form, WhatsApp, or email. As a first step, I offer a free digital audit — evaluating your current digital presence and suggesting custom solutions. There is no commitment required to receive a quote.",
        "about_hero_title": "Alperen Börklü — Web Designer and SEO Specialist",
        "about_hero_lead": "I deliver premium web design, search engine optimization (SEO), and creative brand identity in Ankara, strengthening your brand's authority and visibility in the digital world.",
        "about_sec_subtitle": "Expertise",
        "about_sec_title": "Approach & Methodology",
        "about_h3_title": "Premium Web Design",
        "about_h4_title": "Search Engine Optimization (SEO)",
        "about_h5_title": "Holistic Design & Strategy",
        "about_p3": "As a web designer, I step away from standard templates to develop custom interfaces that truly reflect your brand's identity and corporate goals. In today's competitive digital ecosystem, having a basic website is no longer enough. I design premium digital showcases that set you apart from your competitors, elevate the user experience (UX/UI), and directly convert visitors into clients or business partners. I incorporate luxury details, respected serif typographies like Playfair Display, asymmetric minimalist grid layouts, and fluid micro-animations into your site's visual structure. Furthermore, I build the codebase from scratch using Vanilla JS and modern CSS instead of relying on the bulky infrastructure of ready-made systems like WordPress. This ensures your website is completely secure, ultra-fast, and 100% compliant with Core Web Vitals performance metrics. I approach every design project as a digital work of art that serves your brand's long-term growth vision. To increase user dwell time and drive high conversion rates, I carefully structure every micro-interaction and visual transition on the page.",
        "about_p4": "As an SEO specialist, I ensure that your website secures a permanent high-ranking position on Google through search engine optimization. SEO is not merely about stuffing random keywords into your pages. True organic growth is achieved through a combination of technical SEO setup, ultra-fast page load times, mobile-first responsive coding, user-friendly site architecture, and complete structured data (Schema Markup) implementation. For prestigious law firms and lawyers in Ankara's Çankaya region, I construct article blog infrastructures that are 100% compliant with the Turkish Bar Association (TBB) advertising ban regulations, eliminating disciplinary risks while focusing on informative content marketing. For industrial manufacturers, CNC machining workshops, and defense suppliers in Ostim and Ivedik, I implement multilingual international SEO strategies that connect them directly with B2B buyers worldwide. By targeting the right search queries, I capture the buying intent of your target audience and transform your website from a passive page into an active customer acquisition channel. Through continuous performance tracking, I keep your site ahead of search engine updates.",
        "about_p5": "I combine the systems-oriented design philosophy I acquired through my METU Industrial Design degree with digital marketing and search engine optimization methodologies. This holistic approach provided by Alperen Börklü establishes a strong synergy between visual arts and data analytics. To date, I have successfully managed the digital transformation and brand identity design processes of over 100 local and international brands, alongside collaborating with prominent institutions such as the Goethe Institut, Paribu, TRT Belgesel, and the Ministry of Trade. In my work, instead of chasing short-lived trends, I focus on building a permanent digital asset that will protect your brand's online authority and consistently drive growing organic search traffic for years to come. Blending artistic expression with rigorous analytical methods, I create digital products that leave a lasting impact. In every project, my ultimate goal is to build a high-performance framework that not only captivates users visually but also generates measurable business growth.",
        "services_list_title": "All Services",
